pos_examples: Now, communicate image data of objective rain in mode kumquat from rover roof_11 at waypoint socket to lander screen at waypoint socket_49.
[1] (communicate_image_data roof_11 screen rain kumquat socket socket_49) [2] (communicate_image_data rn k r_11 z abc z_49 o)
Once your done, please sample rock at waypoint object_50 with rover roof_11 and store in store yew.
[1] (sample_rock roof_11 yew object_50) [2] (sample_rock o r_11 yew)
First, drop from store yew of rover roof_11 and then calibrate camera teddy on rover roof_11 for objective rain at waypoint socket.

[1] (drop roof_11 yew) [2] (drop yew r_11)
[1] (calibrate roof_11 teddy rain socket) [2] (calibrate td r_11 rn z)
The next step is to take an image of objective rain in mode kumquat using camera teddy on rover roof_11 from waypoint socket.
[1] (take_image roof_11 socket rain teddy kumquat) [2] (take_image rn k td r_11 z)
